author: wonpoint4
body:
Add new MuonHLT Seed Classifier model files.
The v2 models used the 14 TeV MC samples, so the new models based on the latest MC are needed.
These v3 models are based on the 13.6 TeV 126X Winter23 DY, and Jpsi samples.

The relevant slides during the TSG meeting on 18th Apr.
https://indico.cern.ch/event/1274734/contributions/5353294/subcontributions/422285/attachments/2631130/4550737/230418_TSG_MuonHLT_wonjun.pdf
title: New Model using 126X Winter23 DY+Jpsi
